				<wikidot:authorName>Hydrails-EPSILON</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5348862</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Hmmm&#8230;.</p> <p>starts off on a rather innocuous note ('innocuous' here meaning lacking of knowledge because honestly, the SCP from its description already establishes it as disturbing)</p> <p>But then, the log establishes the real horror of the piece.</p> <p>Though I wonder&#8230; what happened in the last log?</p> <p>(asking, having read stuff related to body horror and real-life disabilities)</p> 
				 	]]>
